text: Baranovka () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Baybeksky Selsoviet, Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 41 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 5 km north from Krasny Yar. == References == Category:Rural localities in Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Baranovka, Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
